data.description: Welcome to the wide open space of 1015 Lakeland Circle sitting on just over 1 acre lot.  If your looking for country living with a modern home this is it!  The single story ranch style home with it's 3 Bedrooms, 2 Full Bathrooms, 1 Guest Half Bath, 3 car side-by-side garage is gorgeous and it's barley lived in, move-in ready.  There are beautiful designer touches throughout the home with stunning flooring, designer hardware and fixtures, tall ceilings, a Kitchen you are going to love creating in and so much natural light throughout the home to give it that "I'm home" comfortable feel.  There is even a screened in patio so you can enjoy gazing out into the Texas skies.  The location couldn't be better with easy proximity to Angleton, Alvin and even Pearland.  288 is just minutes from your driveway.  Call today to schedule your private showing and come feel the country living you've been wanting!
